text.section:
As used in this section:
"Foundation" means a charitable community foundation established to accept gifts, bequests, devises, or other transfers for the purpose of meeting charitable objectives for the citizens of the community;
"Local government" means every city, regardless of classification, every county, and every charter county and urban-county government;
"Component fund" means an individual fund treated as part of a foundation and that meets the requirements established under regulations promulgated implementing 26 U.S.C. sec. 170 as amended from time to time; and
"Nonprofit organization" means an organization incorporated under KRS Chapter 273 and exempt under Section 501(c)(3) of the Internal Revenue Code.
